  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Classify fungi into the five major phyla</item>
<item>Describe each phylum in terms of major representative species and patterns of reproduction</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
